news.news: Reddish (back) is doubtful for Tuesday's game against Dallas, Jovan Buha of The Athletic reports.
news.analysis: Reddish was previously considered questionable, but it appears as though the Lakers will hold him out. In Reddish's expected absence, there could be more minutes available for Dorian Finney-Smith and Dalton Knecht.
